=== Etymology ===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[未伪喂渭慰谓喂魏蠈蟼]]''' (''daemonikos'') "possessed by a demon, sent by a demon", from '''[[未伪委渭蠅谓]]''' (''daemon'') "[[demon]]".

